    "custom_liquid_QWbLRi": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .faq-section {\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n  .faq-title {\n    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 38px);\n    color: #c9836a;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 0 0 36px;\n  }\n  .faq-list {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .faq-item {\n    background: #faf3ef;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .faq-question {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 18px 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-align: left;\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n  .faq-question span {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #222;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .faq-icon {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    color: #aaa;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    transition: transform 0.25s ease;\n    line-height: 1;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n    color: #c9836a;\n  }\n  .faq-answer {\n    max-height: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-answer {\n    max-height: 300px;\n    padding: 0 20px 18px;\n  }\n  .faq-answer p {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #555;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-title\">frequently asked questions</h2>\n  <div class=\"faq-list\">\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>How much coverage does Body Coverage Perfector provide?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>It's fully buildable. One layer evens skin tone and hides redness. Two layers cover scars, bruises, and hyperpigmentation. Three layers conceal deep veins and tattoos — all without looking heavy or unnatural.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Is it really waterproof and sweatproof?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>Yes — clinically proven. Once it sets on clean, oil-free skin, Body Coverage Perfector is waterproof, sweatproof, and transfer-resistant. You can swim, sweat, and go about your day without worrying about touch-ups. To remove, use any oil-based cleanser.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>How do I find the right shade?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>We offer 10 shades ranging from Light Radiance to Rich Radiance. As a general rule, match to your body skin tone — not your face. If you're between shades, go lighter; you can always layer for more depth or mix two shades for a custom match.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>What's the best way to apply it?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>Start with clean, dry, oil-free skin. Apply liberally and blend upward and outward using hands or our Blend & Blur Body Brush. Allow 10 minutes to dry, then buff with a towel or mitt until it no longer transfers. For hard-to-cover areas, apply a first layer as a concealer, then blend a second coat over the full area.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>How long does it last, and how do I remove it?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>When applied correctly on exfoliated, oil-free skin, Body Coverage Perfector is clinically shown to last for days — even through showers. To remove, use an oil-based cleanser like our Makeup Melter Cleansing Oil. Regular soap alone won't fully break it down.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleFaq(btn) {\n    const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');\n    const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));\n    if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n  }\n</script>",
        "full_width": false,
        "show_divider": false,
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_PyWqQE": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  .reviews-section {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    padding: 48px 20px 60px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow-x: hidden;\n  }\n  .reviews-hearts {\n    color: #c9836a;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    letter-spacing: 6px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .reviews-title {\n    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 40px);\n    color: #c9836a;\n    margin: 0 0 32px;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n  }\n  .reviews-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 16px;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  .review-card {\n    background: #faf3ef;\n    border: 1.5px solid #e8ded8;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    text-align: left;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    width: 100%;\n    min-width: 0;\n  }\n  .review-body {\n    padding: 20px;\n    flex: 1;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 8px;\n  }\n  .review-verified {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #c9836a;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    display: block;\n  }\n  .review-stars {\n    color: #c9836a;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    display: block;\n  }\n  .review-title {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111111;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n    margin: 0;\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n    overflow-wrap: break-word;\n  }\n  .review-text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #444444;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0;\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n    overflow-wrap: break-word;\n    white-space: normal;\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  .reviews-toggle {\n    margin-top: 32px;\n    background: none;\n    border: 2px solid #c9836a;\n    color: #c9836a;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.04em;\n    padding: 12px 32px;\n    border-radius: 100px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;\n  }\n  .reviews-toggle:hover {\n    background: #c9836a;\n    color: #ffffff;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 900px) {\n    .reviews-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 560px) {\n    .reviews-section {\n      padding: 36px 16px 48px;\n    }\n    .reviews-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n    .review-body {\n      padding: 18px 16px;\n      gap: 8px;\n    }\n    .review-title {\n      font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .review-text {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      line-height: 1.7;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"reviews-section\">\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-hearts\">♥ ♥ ♥ ♥ ♥</div>\n  <h2 class=\"reviews-title\">Loved by Over 10,000 Women</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Customer</span>\n        <span class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n        <p class=\"review-title\">I can wear shorts again</p>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">I have terrible spider veins from years of nursing. For the past few years I couldn't wear shorts or dresses. This has literally changed my life — it covers everything and stays on all day.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Customer</span>\n        <span class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n        <p class=\"review-title\">Actually waterproof — I tested it</p>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">I did a 4-mile charity walk in 90-degree heat and it didn't budge. Not one streak. I'm in my 60s and can't use self-tanners because of my age spots — this looks completely natural.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Customer</span>\n        <span class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n        <p class=\"review-title\">Looks like skin, not makeup</p>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Golden Radiance is a perfect match for me. My legs look smooth, even, and younger. People never know I'm wearing anything — unless I choose to tell them.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-grid\" id=\"extraReviews\" style=\"display:none; margin-top: 16px;\">\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Customer</span>\n        <span class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n        <p class=\"review-title\">Covers my tattoo completely</p>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">Three layers and my tattoo is completely invisible. I wore it to a formal event and nobody had a clue. Stays put through dancing, heat, everything. Nothing else comes close.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Customer</span>\n        <span class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n        <p class=\"review-title\">My skin looks 30 again</p>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">I have mature, sun-damaged skin with age spots everywhere. Self-tanners just darken them. This covers them evenly and gives me a natural glow. I look and feel like myself again.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <div class=\"review-body\">\n        <span class=\"review-verified\">✓ Verified Customer</span>\n        <span class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n        <p class=\"review-title\">Worth every penny</p>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">I was skeptical at first but the coverage is unreal. Covered bruises, dark spots, and veins without rubbing off on anything. I didn't have to resort to pantyhose for the first time in years.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <button class=\"reviews-toggle\" id=\"reviewsToggle\" onclick=\"toggleReviews()\">\n    See More Reviews ▾\n  </button>\n\n</section>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleReviews() {\n    var extra = document.getElementById('extraReviews');\n    var btn = document.getElementById('reviewsToggle');\n    if (extra.style.display === 'none') {\n      extra.style.display = 'grid';\n      btn.textContent = 'Show Less ▴';\n    } else {\n      extra.style.display = 'none';\n      btn.textContent = 'See More Reviews ▾';\n    }\n  }\n</script>",
        "full_width": true,
        "show_divider": false,
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    }
